---
// ValueProposition.astro — Problem vs Solution comparison with glassmorphism cards
---

<section class="value-prop" id="value-proposition">
  <div class="value-prop-inner">
    <h2 class="value-prop-heading" data-animate>
      Why <span class="accent-text">MIND</span>?
    </h2>
    <p class="value-prop-subtitle" data-animate data-delay="1">
      Knowledge management at scale demands automated consistency verification.
    </p>

    <div class="value-prop-grid">
      <!-- Problem Column -->
      <div class="glass-card value-card value-card-problem" data-animate data-delay="1">
        <h3 class="value-card-title">The Problem</h3>
        <ul class="value-card-list">
          <li>Enterprise knowledge bases accumulate contradictions as they grow</li>
          <li>Manual review is expensive, slow, and error-prone</li>
          <li>Multilingual content multiplies inconsistency risks</li>
          <li>Outdated answers erode user trust and operational reliability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Solution Column -->
      <div class="glass-card value-card value-card-solution" data-animate data-delay="2">
        <h3 class="value-card-title">MIND's Solution</h3>
        <ul class="value-card-list">
          <li><strong>Automated discrepancy detection</strong> across documents and languages</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-LLM backend</strong> for robust, cross-validated analysis</li>
          <li><strong>Polylingual topic modeling</strong> to cluster related content</li>
          <li><strong>Interactive dashboard</strong> for reviewing and resolving findings</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .value-prop {
    padding: var(--spacing-section) 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-prop-inner {
    max-width: var(--container-content);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .value-prop-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-prop-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    max-width: 50ch;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-component);
  }

  .value-prop-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .value-card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card-icon-solution {
    color: var(--color-electric);
  }

  .value-card-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .value-card-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  .value-card-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .value-card-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .value-card-solution .value-card-list li::before {
    background-color: var(--color-electric);
  }

  .value-card-solution strong {
    color: var(--color-electric);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-prop-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .value-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
